title: Irelia with Sheen Q + E's into my Kennen
body:
And dumpsters 50% of my health before I get out of the stun.
Meanwhile, she loses 20% of her health from my entire Q + W + E combo.

How the fuck is Kennen supposed to be viable while he has such shitty 1v1 damage that trading with anything that can gap close or CC is impossible?
